{"tid":1032241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"華為高層：沒有華為的 5g 市場，有如英超沒有曼聯","createTime":"2019-02-22T08:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T08:26:54.000Z","uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ea9bec78b0ddceddd7d7dd7bb5281ebbc072ce","tid":1032241,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:16:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%9A%84-5g-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E6%9C%89%E5%A6%82%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF-%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E9%87%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%96%91%E6%85%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%259A%2584-5g-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25B6%2585%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259B%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BD%2588%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2585%25AE%2F&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=22813de2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%259A%2584-5g-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25B6%2585%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259B%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BD%2588%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2585%25AE%2F&h=47fa6f8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%9A%84-5g-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E6%9C%89%E5%A6%82%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF-%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E9%87%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%96%91%E6%85%AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n華為高層：沒有華為的 5g 市場 有如英超沒有曼聯 將公佈方案釋安全疑慮<br />\n<br />\n美國持續呼籲盟友杯葛中國電訊設備巨頭華為，華為高層、營運商業務總裁丁耘表示，華為今年上半年會公布全球方案，釋除外界對華為產品安全風險的疑慮，他又形容缺乏華為的 5G 市場，「有如英超沒有曼聯」。<br />\n<br />\n丁耘星期四（2月21日）接受訪問時稱，預計在 3 月底前，公司內部會通過一個覆蓋全球，而且全面的方案，釋除不同持份者，包括英國持份者對華為產品的憂慮，預計今年年中前就會正式推出。<br />\n<br />\n丁耘又表示，華為致力在八個方面建立誠信，包括軟件及硬件工程、第三方零件管理和企業文化等，更會為此在全球投資超過 20 億美元，約 157 億港元。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報道形容，在美國全面打壓下，英國成為華為電訊設備一個重要戰場，英國國家網路安全中心即將發表報告，預計亦會提及華為安全問題。丁耘相信報告不會受政治影響，未來華為是否可以參與英國 5G 網結建設，他認為應交由營運商決定，要採用哪些設備供應商，但他形容「沒有華為的 5G 市場，有如英超沒有曼聯。」<br />\n<br />\n魚拉突，啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e2f8800cd4db323ad1e699e779e1ff0b13fd27","tid":1032241,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"華為曲線踩獌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8fcc5f7d39cddf554e4494c833e281e5c4a15d","tid":1032241,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"美國=利物浦"},{"pid":"515fa2d7b854f73e88c72146bb002e1ad3a73a96","tid":1032241,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"sb"},{"pid":"924dcf949ea51c1d37be0fe8848d83fcec9e131d","tid":1032241,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b8fcc5f7d39cddf554e4494c833e281e5c4a15d","tid":1032241,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"美國=利物浦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"美帝一統江湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5849d7df6c7c1d38acb373caee9980519c142bf1","tid":1032241,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:18:48.000Z","msg":"英超沒有獌更好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi